  "description": "This dataset comprises intracranial EEG recordings from 125 patients performing a picture-naming task. Electrode coordinates are provided in MNI-305 stereotactic space. The dataset includes event markers for stimulus onset (401) and response onset (501), enabling analysis of neural dynamics during language production and naming processes.",
  "methods_description": "Intracranial EEG recordings were acquired during a picture-naming task. Event codes mark stimulus onset (401) and response onset (501). Electrode coordinates are registered to MNI-305 space.",
